<h2 class="bold font-l">I'm Through Saving The World</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Jak, still embittered from having been banished from Haven, turns down Ashelin's pleas to return to assist with the war. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RefusalOfTheCall" class='trope-example-link'>Refusal of the Call</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
